thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Sybel Galvan

author: Sybel Galvan
title: Sybel Galvan
text:
I have been ordering eyeglasses from your site the last 3 years.
This is the first time I have to call for a refund in part of my order.
You run out of stock of the frame I order, I wait until the eyeglsses wher produced.
I needed to change the delivery address because of this delay, it was imposible to do it. Last yeat i was able to change delivery address wothout any problema.
I do regret I couldnt have my order complete.
Regards,
